                    <bibl xml:id="bib971-7">ms Damas, Patriarcat syrien orthodoxe, cod. 12/16 (olim Jérusalem, Couvent syrien orthodoxe Saint-Marc, cod. 156 (Baumstark Litur. 43)), f. 179v-180v</bibl>
                </note>
